long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
TabMerge is a simple and efficient tool that finds and removes duplicate tabs, leaving you with a clean and organized browsing experience. With just a few clicks, you can quickly and easily shut down any unnecessary duplicates, saving you time and hassle.

It's also great for saving memory and improving the performance of your browser.
